#: templates/risk/Instructions.html:6
#, python-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You have an endowment of 100 points.  You can choose to invest part of "
#| "this sum in a risky project. If the project goes well, which can happen "
#| "with a probability of 1/2 you will obtain 2.5 points for each point you "
#| "invested. </p><p>If the project fails instead, you'll loose all the "
#| "points invested in it. The points you do not invest will remain to you "
#| "whatever the outcome of the project."
msgid ""
"You have an endowment of 100 points.  You can choose to invest part of this "
"sum in a risky project. If the project goes well, which can happen with a "
"50%% probability you will obtain 2.5 points for each point you invested. </"
"p><p>If the project fails instead, you'll loose all the points invested in "
"it. The points you do not invest will remain to you whatever the outcome of "
"the project."
msgstr ""
"Hai a disposizione 100 punti.  Puoi decidere di investire una parte di "
"questa somma in un progetto rischioso. Se il progetto va bene, cosa che può "
"accadere con probabilità pari al 50%%,  per ogni punto investito otterrai "
"2,5 punti. </p><p>Se invece il progetto va male perderai tutti i punti "
"investiti in esso. I punti che non investi rimarranno a te inalterati quale "
"che sia l'esito del progetto."

